{"tid":1569581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼915還要上街，每次民陣當我地condom","createTime":"2019-09-14T16:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:03:48.000Z","uid":17400,"like":4,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ec72ad8bead57f9e17891c8e44293e5a02219e53","tid":1569581,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:14:49.000Z","msg":"而家出街遊行 民陣當我地condom咋<br />\n<br />\n根本就冇用  次次又係比班鬼/黑警搞死場遊行  <br />\n人又走唔到 去又去唔到 <br />\n次次出去 <br />\n 一係就中環行到銅鑼灣搭車 <br />\n一係就銅鑼灣行到中環搭車 <br />\n同埋 英國根本冇人想理你香港 <br />\n而家唔係要拎Bno 黎打飛機  <br />\n英國脫歐都自求多福啦  <br />\n<br />\n而家 封路 堵路 放火燒地 唱下歌 整連儂牆 叫口號 拖人鏈 係有民心 但...冇用啊大佬  <br />\n就算有200-300萬人再上街都冇用  <br />\n唔係多一個人就多一個人  <br />\n出一個就多一個落單  <br />\n發完夢 第二日未繼續返工返學 <br />\n對唔準政權 對唔準黑警<br />\n只會警黑合作 警藍合作 每日上映 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d33f9187d9b42b7dd598e2d748d086012626068","tid":1569581,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0183f1dee77a39d849b41f74992b97bfa7a15540","tid":1569581,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:15:48.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a0e990125377e93a01a741bde41f4a4920f9748d","tid":1569581,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"bb0e799fb82d3c6113a0f2fbc938c8f77b012a47","tid":1569581,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"b6a2de7d92615608a39ce10f1d8aafa2e3c24e7c","tid":1569581,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007cb149d3fda3f9032a6aca43b9c3bc3cb